{"tid":1875701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上頂推比傳媒] 政府內部評估疫情搞幾個月？停課停幾個月？","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T14:31:20.000Z","uid":77040,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"832780d3882654da805fc1457bdd0d1ec3da2dc7","tid":1875701,"uid":77040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"教師手足收到份咁既野，好奇怪，<br />\n唔通政府內部評估疫情搞幾個月？停課停幾個月？<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，教育局旗下的教師中心選舉本身投票期係1/23 - 2/14<br />\n因為停課影響, 本來係復課後兩星期內完成投票(3/1-3/13)<br />\n但琴日突然間出份咁既野，話改為下學年先投票,即係9月-10月<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明明本身復課後兩個禮拜就做完既野，點解突然間要拖到9月先投票？<br />\n投個票詐wor, 有mug野咁影響學校運作？<br />\n唔通政府內部評估個疫症令到停課停幾個月？</span></span></strong><br />\nOXY 又唔封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n份文件：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgiQzOR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgiQzOR.png&h=d2cbf046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來投票係復課後兩星期內完成(3/1-3/13)<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cp9HqVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCp9HqVw.png&h=f452a884&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aj9HqVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAj9HqVw.png&h=9b64acd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41550d62b01b85bbe6983c3ec240d33a7e8fc069","tid":1875701,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"大佬，停咗咁耐 就算3月復課，都好撚多嘢做架，你估復課就淨係上返堂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c7264dd5b9e23c88bafae94c3cc6bbc9e191fe","tid":1875701,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0