 />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但首要都係要夾佢封關先！<br />\n所以要先爆佢老味，政府自己知疫症分分鐘搞幾個月，又唔封關！<br />\n夾佢交代政府自己評估左d mug!!!!<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c741575ec4468dc71a0189a22a8e681acc5ded4a","tid":1875701,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a07647d86fafacc1965a835bdacd982ce8947478","tid":1875701,"uid":33712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"未必關事<br />\n今年教協拉隊選嘛"},{"pid":"e0c4109ac3ce6631fe25b95730c4e3d6fb5da46c","tid":1875701,"uid":77040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a07647d86fafacc1965a835bdacd982ce8947478","tid":1875701,"uid":33712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"未必關事<br />\n今年教協拉隊選嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，即係借疫症搞彎個選舉，黑箱作業，都係hihi。我覺得疫情評估(但又hi佢個hi唔封關)定係黑箱作業，兩個可能性都有。而家個時勢，我會選擇相信疫情評估，罵爆佢，局佢封關先最重要。<br />\n<br />\n佢否認咗係疫情評估問題，再爆佢黑箱作業都未遲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}